          EN: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask the patient about their personal information.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient Profile. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>4. Patient's Name (Last Name, First Name, MI, Extension)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask the patient about their personal information.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient Profile. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Pangalan (Apelyido, Unang Pangalan, Gitnang Inisyal, Ext.)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask the patient about their personal information.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient Profile. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Pangaran (Apelyido, Pangaran, MI, Ext.)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask the patient about their personal information.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient Profile. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Ngalan sa Pasyente (Apelyido, Ngalan, Middle Initial, Extension)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Before proceeding to the survey proper, we would like to ask the patient about their personal information.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient Profile. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Ngalan sa Pasyente (Apelyido, Pangalan, MI, Extension)</p>
