  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q6_AGE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>6. Just to confirm, how old is the patient as of his/her last birthday? (in years)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Para lamang makumpirma, ilang taong gulang ang pasyente noong huling kaarawan niya? (sa taon)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pira an edad mo base sa huring kaarawan mo? (sa taon)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Aron makumpirma, pila ang edad sa pasyente base sa iyang pinakaulahi nga adlawng natawhan? (sa tuig)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Para ma-confirm lang, pila na ang edad sa pasyente base sa iyang miaging birthday? (sa tuig)</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Para la makumpirma, pira na an edad han pasyente tikang han iya urhi nga kaadlawan? (ha mga tuig)</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q7_SEX
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>7. What is the patient's sex at birth?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang kasarian ng pasyente noong ipinanganak?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ano an saimong kasarian kan ika tig aki?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa ang sex sa pasyente sa pagkatawo?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang sex sa pasyente sa pagkahimugso?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an sekso han pasyente han katawo?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q8_LGBTQIA
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kabilang ba ang pasyente sa komunidad ng LGBTQIA+? (hal., gay, lesbian, bisexual, atbp.) Walang problema at naiintidihan namin kung hindi komportable na sumagot.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>8. Is the patient part of the LGBTQIA+ community? (e.g., gay, lesbian, bisexual, etc.). It is fine if not comfortable answering.</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
