  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q10_CIVIL_STATUS
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>10. What is the patient's civil status?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang katayuang sibil ng pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Ano an saimong civil status?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa ang sibil nga status sa pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang civil status sa pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an sibil nga kahimtang han pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q11_PWD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>11. Does the patient identify as a person with a disability?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang pasyente ba ay isang taong may kapansanan?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An pasyente ba ay may disability?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pasyente ba giila nga siya usa ka tawo nga adunay kapansanan?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nagpaila ba ang pasyente isip usa ka tawo nga adunay kapansanan/PWD?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nag-iidentify ba an pasyente nga may kapansanan?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q12_PWD_SPECIFY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>12. Would the patient like to specify the type of disability?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kung nais ng pasyente, maaari bang tukuyin ang uri ng kapansanan?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong klaseng diability igwa an pasyente?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Okay lang ba sa pasyente nga hisgutan o i-specify ang klase sa iyang kapansanan?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Gusto ba sa pasyente isulti kung unsa nga klase sa kapansanan?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Karuyag ba ig-specify or isumat han pasyente an klase han kapansanan?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q13_PWD_CARD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>13. May we view the patient's PWD Identification Card?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Maaari ba naming makita ang PWD Identification (ID) Card ng pasyente?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pwede mi ba mahiling an PWD ID card kan pasyente?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pwede ba namo makita ang PWD ID sa pasyente?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Pwede ba mi makakita sa PWD Identification Card sa pasyente?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Pwede ba namon makita an PWD nga Kard han Pasyente?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q14_DISABILITY_TYPE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>14. Based on the presented PWD Identification Card, what type of disability is indicated?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Batay sa ipinakitang PWD Identification Card, ano ang uri ng kapansanan na nakasaad?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Base sa tigpresenta na PWD ID Card, anong disability ang nakalaag?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Base sa gipresentar nga PWD Identification Card, unsa nga klase sa kapansanan ang gipakita?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Base han iginpresentar nga PWD Identification Card, ano nga klase hin kapansanan an iginpapakita?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator Instruction (DO NOT READ ALOUD): If the PWD Identification Card is presented, record the type of disability as indicated on the card. Do not ask the respondent directly.</p>
