  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q38_PHILHEALTH_REG
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm their PhilHealth registration status and membership, and their registration to other health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>38. Are you currently registered with PhilHealth?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang mga susunod na tanong ay tungkol sa karanasan ng pasyente sa pagpaparehistro sa PhilHealth. Kukumpirmahin din namin ang status ng pagpaparehistro at pagiging miyembro sa PhilHealth, pati na rin ang kanilang pagpaparehistro sa iba pang health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Sa kasalukuyan ba ay nakarehistro kayo sa PhilHealth?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm their PhilHealth registration status and membership, and their registration to other health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Ika ba ay rehistrado sa Philhealth?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm their PhilHealth registration status and membership, and their registration to other health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Karon ba, rehistrado ka sa PhilHealth?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm their PhilHealth registration status and membership, and their registration to other health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Nakarehistro ba ka karon sa PhilHealth?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s PhilHealth registration experience. We will also confirm their PhilHealth registration status and membership, and their registration to other health insurance.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s PhilHealth Registration and Health Insurance. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies.</p><p>Nakarehistro ka ba yana ha PhilHealth?</p>
