          BIS: |
            <p>Unsang klase sa primary care facility ang pinakaduol sa inyong balay?</p><p class="instruction">An institution that primarily delivers primary care services or the initial-contact facility for coordinated care (e.g., RHU, health center, general practitioner clinic).</p>
