  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q83_VISIT_REASON
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now be asking about the patient’s actions taken for health concerns. This includes the type of services and facilities they access for their health and well-being.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>83. What best describes why the patient visited a health facility (e.g. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Magtatanong kami ngayon tungkol sa mga ginawa ng pasyente na pangkalusugan. Kabilang dito ang uri ng mga serbisyong ginagamit at mga pasilidad na pinupuntahan para sa kalusugan at kagalingan.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>Ano ang pangunahing dahilan kung bakit bumisita ang pasyente sa pasilidad? (hal. RHU, health center, klinika, ospital)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now be asking about the patient’s actions taken for health concerns. This includes the type of services and facilities they access for their health and well-being.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>Ano an pinaka-rason kung gnata pigdumanan mo an facility (hal. RHU, health center, clinic, hospital)?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now be asking about the patient’s actions taken for health concerns. This includes the type of services and facilities they access for their health and well-being.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>Unsay labing hinungdan nganong mubisita and pasyente sa usa ka pasilidad sa panglawas (Pananglitam: RHU, clinic,hospital)?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now be asking about the patient’s actions taken for health concerns. This includes the type of services and facilities they access for their health and well-being.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>Unsa ang labing maayong paghulagway nganong mibisita ang pasyente sa usa ka pasilidad sa panglawas (pananglitan, RHU, health center, clinic, ospital)?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now be asking about the patient’s actions taken for health concerns. This includes the type of services and facilities they access for their health and well-being.</p><p class="instruction">Note to enumerator [do not read]: This section is for the Patient’s Health-Seeking Behavior. Ask all questions in this section unless a skip rule applies. READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p><p>READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
