  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q97_FINAL_AMOUNT
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>97. What was the final amount you paid in cash for your outpatient care? (Amount in Pesos)</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Magkano ang kabuuang halagang binayaran mo nang cash para sa iyong outpatient care?</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>97. What was the final amount you paid in cash for your outpatient care? (Amount in Pesos)</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pila ang kinatibuk-ang kantidad nga imong gibayad cash para sa imong outpatient care?</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa ang katapusang kantidad nga imong gibayran og cash para sa imong outpatient care?</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an katapusan nga kantidad nga imo ginbayad nga cash para han imo pag-ataman ha gawas?</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
