  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q99_BUCAS_HEARD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about BUCAS and the services they accessed in a BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>99. Have you heard about Bagong Urgent Care and Ambulatory Services (BUCAS) center?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Magtatanong kami ngayon tungkol sa kaalaman ng pasyente sa BUCAS at sa mga serbisyong natanggap sa isang BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Narinig ba ninyo ang Bagong Urgent Care at Ambulatory Service (BUCAS) center?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about BUCAS and the services they accessed in a BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nadangog mo na ba an Bagong Urgent Care and Ambulatory Service (BUCAS)?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about BUCAS and the services they accessed in a BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Bagong Urgent Care and Ambulatory Services (BUCAS) center?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about BUCAS and the services they accessed in a BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Bagong Urgent Care and Ambulatory Services (BUCAS) center?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about BUCAS and the services they accessed in a BUCAS Center.</p><p class="instruction">Q99 to Q103 are applicable only to respondents in areas with BUCAS center. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nakabati ka na ba mahitungod han Bagong Urgent Care and Ambulatory Services (BUCAS) center?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q100_BUCAS_SOURCE_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>100. If yes, what are your sources of information about this BUCAS center? — News</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang inyong mga pinagkukunan ng impormasyon tungkol sa BUCAS center? — Ano ang inyong mga pinagkukunan ng impormasyon tungkol sa BUCAS center? — Balita</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Balita / News</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>100. If yes, what are your sources of information about this BUCAS center? — News</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Balita</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Balita</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q100_BUCAS_SOURCE_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>100. If yes, what are your sources of information about this BUCAS center? — Legislation</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang inyong mga pinagkukunan ng impormasyon tungkol sa BUCAS center? — Ano ang inyong mga pinagkukunan ng impormasyon tungkol sa BUCAS center? — Batas</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Batas / Legislation</p>
          BIS: |
