  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Not a PhilHealth member</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>(If PhilHealth was not availed in Q113) Bakit hindi mo ginamit ang PhilHealth benefits? (Kung hindi ginamit ang PhilHealth sa tanong 113) — Hindi miyembro ng PhilHealth</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Bako Philhealth member</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Dili miyembro sa PhilHealth</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dili miyembro sa PhilHealth</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Diri miyembro han PhilHealth</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — PhilHealth member but not eligible for benefits</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>(If PhilHealth was not availed in Q113) Bakit hindi mo ginamit ang PhilHealth benefits? (Kung hindi ginamit ang PhilHealth sa tanong 113) — Miyembro ng PhilHealth pero hindi kwalipikado sa benefits</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Member kan Philhealth pero bako siya eligibile kan benefits</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Miyembro sa PhilHealth pero dili eligible sa benepisyo</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Miyembro sa PhilHealth pero dili eligible sa mga benepisyo</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Miyembro han PhilHealth pero diri kwalipikado han mga benepisyo</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Probably used PhilHealth but cannot remember amount because benefit was deducted upon discharge from hospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>(If PhilHealth was not availed in Q113) Bakit hindi mo ginamit ang PhilHealth benefits? (Kung hindi ginamit ang PhilHealth sa tanong 113) — Maaaring ginamit ang PhilHealth pero hindi matandaan ang halaga dahil na-deduct ng madischarge sa ospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Probably used PhilHealth but cannot remember amount because benefit was deducted upon discharge from hospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Tingali nagamit ang PhilHealth pero dili na mahinumduman ang kantidad kay gi-deduct na ang benepisyo pag-discharge sa ospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Tingali nakagamit og PhilHealth pero dili mahinumduman ang kantidad kay gi-deduct na ang benepisyo paggawas sa ospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Siguro gingamit an PhilHealth pero diri nahinunumduman an kantidad kay gin-ibanan an benepisyo paggawas ha ospital</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q114_NO_PH_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>114. Why did you not avail of PhilHealth benefits? (If PhilHealth was not availed in 113) — Too many requirements to comply with before can avail</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>(If PhilHealth was not availed in Q113) Bakit hindi mo ginamit ang PhilHealth benefits? (Kung hindi ginamit ang PhilHealth sa tanong 113) — Maraming requirements bago magamit ang benefits</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          BCL: |
