          BIS: |
            <p>Daghan kaayong requirements nga kinahanglan comply-an sa dili pa maka-avail</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Daghan kaayo og mga requirement nga kinahanglan i-comply una maka-avail</p><p class="instruction">If patient provides a receipt, select all that apply. If no receipt was provided, read options out loud. Select all that apply. If yes, indicate the amount spent.</p>
          WAR: |
