          WAR: |
            <p>The following questions relate to the patient’s most recent experience with ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ as an [inpatient] or [outpatient], where we invited you to participate in our survey on [date_formatted].</p><p>Mga lugar hin paghulat</p>
