  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q135_SAT_OVERALL_TIME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>135. Were you satisfied with the overall time spent from registration to exiting the facility? (For inpatients only)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Nasiyahan ka ba sa kabuuang oras na ginugol mula sa pagpaparehistro hanggang sa paglabas sa pasilidad?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Were you satisfied with the overall time spent from registration to exiting the facility?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Giganahan ba ka sa kinatibuk-ang oras nga imong gigahin gikan sa pag rehistro hangtud sa pag gawas sa pasilidad?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kontento ba ka sa kinatibuk-ang oras nga gigugol gikan sa pagparehistro hangtod sa paggawas sa pasilidad?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kuntento ka ba han kabug-usan nga oras nga gingamit tikang ha pagparehistro tubtob ha paggawas ha pasilidad?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q136_STAFF_COURTESY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>136. In most recent visit, how often did the staff treat you with courtesy and respect?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>tinatrato ka ba ng may paggalang at kagandahang asal ng mga staff?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nagpailing saimo nin may respeto asin kabaitan?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>gitratar ka uban ang pagtahod ug maayong pagtagad?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa pinakaulahing pagbisita sa pasyente, unsa ka sagad ang mga kawani mitagad kanimo uban sa maayong pamatasan ug pagrespeto?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Gintratar ka hin matinalahuron ngan may respeto?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q137_STAFF_LISTEN
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>137. In most recent visit, how often did the staff listen carefully to what you say or ask?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>pinapakinggan ka ba nang mabuti ng mga staff sa iyong sinasabi o itinatanong?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Maingat na nagdangog sa saimong sinasabi o tinatanong?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>naminaw pag-ayo sa imong gisulti o gipangutana?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa pinakaulahing pagbisita sa pasyente, unsa ka sagad ang mga kawani maminaw pag-ayo sa imong gisulti o gipangutana?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Namamati hin maupay han imo ginyayakan ngan ginpapakiana?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q138_STAFF_EXPLAIN
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>138. In most recent visit, how often did the staff explain your condition and procedures in a way you can understand?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>ipinaliwanag ba sa iyo ang iyong kalagayan at mga gagawin sa paraang iyong maiintindihan?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nag-explain kan saimong kondisyon asin mga proseso sa paraang madali mong maintindihan?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>gipasabut ang imong kondisyon ug mga proseso sa paagi nga imong masabtan?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>mipasabot sa imong kondisyon ug mga pamaagi sa paagi nga imong masabtan?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Iginsasaysay an imo kahimtang ngan an mga pamaagi nga kon diin imo maiintindihan?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q139_STAFF_DECIDE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>139. In most recent visit, how often did the staff give you the chance to make decisions about your treatment?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>binigyan ka ba ng pagkakataon na makagawa ng desisyon tungkol sa iyong pagpapagamot?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nagtao saimo nin pagkakataon na magdesisyon manungod sa saimong gamutan?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>gihatagan ka og higayon nga makahimog desisyon bahin sa imong pagtambal?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>mihatag kanimo og higayon nga makadesisyon bahin sa imong pagtambal?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Naghahatag haimo hin higayon nga magdesisyon mahitungod han imo pagtambal?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q140_STAFF_CONSENT
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>140. In most recent visit, how often did the staff ask you for your consent before performing any treatments or tests?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>tinanong ka ba para sa iyong pahintulot bago isagawa ang anumang paggamot o pagsusuri?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Naghagad saimo nin pahintulot bago maggibo nin anomang pagbulong o test?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>nangayo sa imong pagtugot (consent) sa dili pa maghimo og bisan unsang pagtambal o test?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>nangayo sa imong pagtugot sa dili pa mohimo og bisan unsang pagtambal o eksaminasyon?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>140. In most recent visit, how often did the staff ask you for your consent before performing any treatments or tests?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q141_CONFIDENTIALITY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>141. In your most recent visit, did the staff assure you that information about the patient's condition will be kept confidential?</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Sa iyong pinakahuling pagbisita, tiniyak ba sa iyo ng mga staff na mananatiling kumpidensyal ang impormasyon tungkol sa kalagayan ng pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sa imong pinakabag-o nga pagbisita, gisiguro ba sa staff nga ang impormasyon bahin sa kondisyon sa pasyente magpabiling kompidensyal?</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa imong pinakaulahing pagbisita, gisiguro ba sa mga kawani nga ang impormasyon bahin sa kondisyon sa pasyente magpabiling kompidensyal?</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Haimo pinakabag-o nga pagbisita, ginpasarig ka ba han tinapuran nga titipigan nga kompidensyal an impormasyon mahitungod han kahimtang han pasyente?</p><p class="instruction">For example, they did not disclose any of your private medical information to anyone not involved in your care.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q142_PRIVACY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>142. In your most recent visit, did the staff respect your privacy during the physical consultation?</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Sa iyong pinakahuling pagbisita, nirespeto ba ng mga staff ang iyong privacy habang isinasagawa ang pisikal na konsultasyon?</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sa imong pinakabag-o nga pagbisita, gitahod ba sa staff ang imong pribasiya panahon sa pisikal nga konsultasyon?</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa imong pinakaulahing pagbisita, gitahod ba sa mga kawani ang imong pribasiya atol sa pisikal nga konsulta?</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ha imo pinakabag-o nga pagbisita, ginrespeto ba han mga staff an imo pribado nga kinabuhi durante han pisikal nga konsultasyon?</p><p class="instruction">For example, your consultation was done in a private area, and no one could overhear your private medical information.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q143_RECOMMEND
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>143. Overall, would you recommend ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ to a friend or relative?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Sa kabuuan, irerekomenda mo ba ang ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ sa kaibigan o kamag-anak?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Sa kabuuan, irerekomenda mo ba an ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ sa sarong kaibigan o kamag-anak?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Sa kinatibuk-an, irekomenda ba nimo ang ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ ngadto sa usa ka higala o paryente?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Sa kinatibuk-an, irekomenda ba nimo ang ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ sa usa ka higala o paryente?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ha kabug-usan, magrerekomenda ka ba [ngaran han pasilidad] ha sangkay o paryente?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q144_QUALITY
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>144. How would the patient rate the quality of care you received at ~~FACILITY_NAME~~?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Paano mo ilalarawan ang kasiyahan bilang pasyente ang kalidad ng pangangalagang natanggap mo sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Paano mo tatawan nin rating an kalidad kan pag-asikaso na narecibe mo sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsay imong i-rate/grado sa kalidad sa pag-atiman kanimo ~~FACILITY_NAME~~?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsaon sa pasyente pag-rate ang kalidad sa pag-atiman nga imong nadawat sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Paonan-o ihahatag han pasyente an kalidad han pag-ataman nga imo nakarawat [ngaran han pasilidad]?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q145_PURCHASE_FREQ
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. We will also ask some questions about their views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>145. How often do you purchase or receive medicines?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang mga susunod na tanong ay may kaugnayan sa access ng pasyente sa mga gamot. Nais naming malaman kung gaano kadali o kahirap na bumili o tumanggap ng mga gamot. Magtatanong din kami ng ilang katanungan tungkol sa kanilang pananaw sa pagbili ng generic o branded na gamot.</p><p>Gaano kadalas kang bumibili o tumatanggap ng mga gamot?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. We will also ask some questions about their views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Mga pirang beses ka magbakal o makaresibi ki bulong?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. We will also ask some questions about their views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Kapila ka kasagaran mupalit o mangayo ug mga tambal?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. We will also ask some questions about their views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Unsa ka sagad ka mopalit o modawat og mga tambal?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>The next questions we will be asking are related to the patient’s access to medicines. We would like to know how easy or difficult it is for them to purchase or receive medicines. We will also ask some questions about their views in buying generic or branded medicines.</p><p>Ano kaagsob ka pumalit o kumarawat hin mga medisina?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q146_RX_OR_OTC
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>146. Was the most recent medicine purchased prescribed by a doctor or over-the-counter (OTC) medicine (no need for a prescription)?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang pinakahuling gamot na binili ba ay inireseta ng doktor o over-the-counter na gamot (hindi kailangan ng reseta)?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong bulong an binakal mo sa ngonyan tigprescribe saimo kan doctor o over-the-counter (OTC) na bulong (dai kaipuhan ki reseta)?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pinakabag-o nga tambal nga imong napalit, gireseta ba kini sa doktor o over-the-counter (OTC) nga tambal (dili kinahanglan og reseta)?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang pinakaulahing tambal nga imong gipalit ba gi-reseta sa doktor o over-the-counter (OTC) nga tambal (dili na kinahanglan og reseta)?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Amo ba an pinakabag-o nga medisina nga ginpalit nga iginreseta han doktor o usa nga waray reseta (OTC)( dire kinahanglan hin reseta)?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q147_MEDS_LIST
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>147. What are the medications that you usually take?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang mga gamot na karaniwan mong iniinom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Anong mga medisina an pirmi na tigabakal asin tigainom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Unsa nga mga tambal ang imong kasagarang ginainom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano it mga medisina nga imo kasagaran gin-iinom?</p><p class="instruction">PLEASE LIST DOWN ALL MEDICINES THAT YOU TOOK FOR THE HEALTH CONDITION.</p>
