  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q152_GAMOT_HEARD
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about the GAMOT package and the medicines they availed in a GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>152. Have you heard of the Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, which is part of PhilHealth's YAKAP/Konsulta or primary care benefit package?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Itatanong namin ngayon ang tungkol sa kaalaman ng pasyente sa GAMOT package at sa mga gamot na nakuha sa isang GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Narinig mo na ba ang Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, na bahagi ng PhilHealth YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package ng PhilHealth?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about the GAMOT package and the medicines they availed in a GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>An masunod na kahapotan ay manungod sa GAMOT Package, kun anong parte kan Philhealth’s YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about the GAMOT package and the medicines they availed in a GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, nga kabahin sa YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package sa PhilHealth?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about the GAMOT package and the medicines they availed in a GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nakadungog na ba ka bahin sa Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) Package, nga parte sa YAKAP/Konsulta o primary care benefit package sa PhilHealth?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We will now ask about the patient’s awareness about the GAMOT package and the medicines they availed in a GAMOT pharmacy.</p><p class="instruction">Q152 to Q157, Q159 are applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT. Otherwise, skip.</p><p>Nabatian mo na ba an Guaranteed and Accessible Medical for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) package, nga kaparte han kanan Philhealth YAKAP/ Konsulta o primary care benefit package?</p>
