  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q154_GAMOT_UNDERSTAND_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>154. What is your understanding of the GAMOT Package? — Provides free or affordable medicines for outpatients</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang iyong pagkaunawa tungkol sa Programang GAMOT? — Nagbibigay ng libre o abot-kayang gamot para sa mga pasyenteng hindi kailangang maospital</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nagtataong libre o affordable na medisina para sa outpatients</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Naghatag og libre o baratuhon nga tambal alang sa mga outpatient</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nagahatag og libre o barato nga mga tambal para sa mga outpatient</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Naghahatag hin libre o barato nga medisina para ha mga pasyente ha gawas</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q154_GAMOT_UNDERSTAND_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>154. What is your understanding of the GAMOT Package? — Ensures continuous availability of essential medicines</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang iyong pagkaunawa tungkol sa Programang GAMOT? — Tinitiyak ang tuloy-tuloy na pagkakaroon ng mahahalagang gamot</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Sigurado an tuloy-tuloy na availability kan essential medicines</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nagsiguro sa padayon nga pagkaanaa sa mga importanteng tambal</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nagsiguro nga kanunay adunay magamit nga mga importanteng tambal</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nagsisiguro hin pakadto nga pagkaada hin importante nga medisina</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q154_GAMOT_UNDERSTAND_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>154. What is your understanding of the GAMOT Package? — Helps reduce out-of-pocket expenses for medicines</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang iyong pagkaunawa tungkol sa Programang GAMOT? — Tinutulungang mabawasan ang sariling gastusin para sa gamot</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nakakatabang makaminos kan out-of-pocket expenses para sa medisina</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nakatabang sa pagpakunhod sa out-of-pocket nga gasto sa tambal</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Makatabang sa pagpaminos sa gasto sa tambal gikan sa kaugalingong bulsa</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nakakabulig nga maibanan an gastos ha bulsa para ha mga medisina</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
