    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>154. What is your understanding of the GAMOT Package? — Supports treatment of common illnesses and chronic conditions</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang iyong pagkaunawa tungkol sa Programang GAMOT? — Sumusuporta sa paggamot ng karaniwang sakit at pangmatagalang karamdaman</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nakakatabang sa pagbulong kan common na mga helang asin chronic conditions</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nagsuporta sa pagtambal sa kasagarang sakit ug chronic conditions</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Nagsuporta sa pagtambal sa kasagarang sakit ug mga chronic nga kondisyon</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
