  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q155_GAMOT_GOT_MEDS
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>155. Did you get the medicines from the GAMOT Package during the past 6 months?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Nakuha mo ba ang mga gamot mula sa GAMOT Package noong nakaraang 6 na buwan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nakakuha kaba kan mga medisina hali sa GAMOT Package kan nakaagi 6 anom na bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Nakakuha ba ka og tambal gikan sa GAMOT Package sulod sa milabay nga 6 ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nakakuha ka ba han mga medisina tikang ha GAMOT Package han naglabay nga unom(6) ka bulan?</p><p class="instruction">Enumerator: Applicable only to respondents in areas with GAMOT.</p>
