  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q172_PCP_REFERRAL
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>172. Was the visit to ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ a referral from your primary care facility?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang pagbisita ba sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ ay referral mula sa iyong pangunahing pasilidad ng pangangalagang pangkalusugan?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>An pagbisita mo ba sa sarong referral ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ gikan sa saimong primary care facility?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang imong pagbisita ba sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ usa ka referral gikan sa imong primary care facility?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang pagbisita ba sa ~~FACILITY_NAME~~ usa ka referral gikan sa imong primary care facility?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An pagbisita ba ha [ngaran_han_pasilidad] in pagrefer tikang han iyo pasilidad han panguna nga pag-ataman?</p>
  - name: PATIENTSURVEY_DICT.Q173_PCP_KNOWS
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>173. Does your primary care provider know that you made the visit?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Alam ba ng iyong pangunahing health provider na bumisita ka roon?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Aram ba kan saimong primary care provider na nagbisita ka?</p>
          BIS: |
